<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:14
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='363000' id='t-363000'>And finally, India has had</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='366000' id='t-366000'>the deepening of its democracy.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='368000' id='t-368000'>When democracy came to India 60 years back</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='370000' id='t-370000'>it was an elite concept.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='372000' id='t-372000'>It was a bunch of people who wanted to bring in democracy</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='375000' id='t-375000'>because they wanted to bring in the idea of</span>
