<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='381000' id='t-381000'>But today democracy has become a bottom-up process</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='384000' id='t-384000'>where everybody has realized</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='386000' id='t-386000'>the benefits of having a voice,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='388000' id='t-388000'>the benefits of being in an open society.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='391000' id='t-391000'>And therefore democracy has become embedded.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:44
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='393000' id='t-393000'>I believe these six factors --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='395000' id='t-395000'>the rise of the notion of population as human capital,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='398000' id='t-398000'>the rise of Indian entrepreneurs,</span>
