<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='409000' id='t-409000'>to why India is today growing</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='411000' id='t-411000'>at rates it has never seen before.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:04
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='413000' id='t-413000'>But having said that,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='415000' id='t-415000'>then we come to what I call as ideas in progress.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='417000' id='t-417000'>Those are the ideas where there is no argument in a society,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='420000' id='t-420000'>but you are not able to implement those things.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='423000' id='t-423000'>And really there are four things here.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='425000' id='t-425000'>One is the question of education.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='427000' id='t-427000'>For some reason, whatever reason -- lack of money,</span>
